parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure in Steering Column
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system in the steering column can cause smoke to emanate from the column, leading to reduced visibility, and in some cases, fires, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Smoke coming from the steering column
smoke or fire in the steering wheel column
